    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "Goals"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Prevent accidental destructive actions.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Ensure destructive buttons are fully accessible (WCAG 2.1 Level AA compliant).",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Create a consistent, predictable pattern across all products.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Educate internal teams on the importance of accessible destructive design.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "Approach"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "🔍 User Testing & Heuristic Analysis"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "We conducted usability testing and heuristic evaluations on key interfaces (e.g., account settings, file managers). Key findings included:"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Users skipped warning text due to poor contrast or vague language.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Keyboard users struggled to locate the active button due to missing focus indicators.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "On mobile, destructive buttons were too close to primary actions like “Save.”",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "img",
      "url": "https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/052b5715-3363-4fe6-980e-3f0dd8222353/1b7c1e25-c1dd-48c8-aa4c-de3e691c5edb/653shots_so.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UWH6YDSB%2F20260324%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260324T145512Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEM%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQCqxXdtVJkhEky1MOiYhVvfbwZNK7n4I0vgzCHBTVVMSQIgVoy5kaXu9KqdjCltLXS6LdrIbbtd7W5kjDp5vYuxeqMqiAQImP%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDFzcqYrCnNGcA7Yy9CrcA5g3RogEhPEsIQ5K4fpeR%2F50uXOu%2BMq1Y0p%2BN%2FVjbAAkvHUEaYQjwUzrJ01tmYNM2J6ogigjcED%2FjAiitlk65X%2BHJ1jKJe5LOapMYglAXShwhEuT3zarahg9np854ISfzr7RJNTx%2B7FDQiVwviCTEIPS1R21kux0T1aH%2BklzjV2ZFYH04Xvxeq%2Bs%2BijVtz5Et%2FjQvE3b8qWHz0joWmXNV%2FjPB2GqoNqahjCvzXk42KA6jXQxSb%2FF9Qdki%2F1PA6jhv4%2BtLnw56Rt7nAr0K5xe7RvB6IbebPy2dwRiXBkCYWr3TipGzcl3fKiNK0WhqTDrkhHY0LY1IaSYeYrcL1%2BMr%2FBPFdnh3V8UXH3rxN5uyoEz5A%2Bj04j%2BxLu%2BE07XeGOZGNcHvibFHT2VrEOJj%2BbbwGY6Cbi%2B4IhWKNhYxg2OnqOYDqxPTNLf0z%2BuhRoQQCWebTH%2FBpaoSP%2BAhPBZRYv3qeGiuhge45w6wCTJ4kUEdt%2BAyi3DTe10gyiQ%2F5vQ4z5avpcXoX9Vb%2Bsf4m%2F2SBghmduixvILqZMvYYqwtv8WLBkWk6yyU1Zt%2BT47OorBerdEQly47wUx7dwywAeJ3jtYu4M23Wf1XZs0fMQX%2BxY%2Bcg%2BBkFiPbzukFW2uECiIMJ7Ais4GOqUBacEjj8GpbD83pteKKVeMC8xgE0gMcMoSiw00InE1zIb%2Bp2AtzV5Y5CY2ASf5gMUNFSbWWO1Rvo6TDNvd86qaNCPYKdJvolf7IAQvTWGkdHpFdMOqVCnYWLudv3grGoIv%2BE00qP5Sa9Oyrk%2FXhY7fEuVqigALxDTuOFWFkM2tjr2jfCpe03MXA1lCXIKFISKezRn%2BRaxSjaZg9wsi21mM%2BHaLYaBj&X-Amz-Signature=a956af25bc40dc2c3585e1da97662e8d7a9d2ea70db52422c1c2df1f19c1fee5&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "h2",
      "text": "Solutions & Design Decisions"
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "Clear, Action-Oriented Labels"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Problem: Vague labels like “Proceed” confused users."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Solution:"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "We replaced ambiguous labels with explicit action verbs, such as:"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "“Delete My Account”",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "“Remove User”",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "“Cancel Subscription”",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "This increased user understanding and reduced hesitation during task completion."
    },
    {
      "type": "img",
      "url": "https://prod-files-secure.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/052b5715-3363-4fe6-980e-3f0dd8222353/30e0ed24-8739-4698-b69a-77c2fde27af7/image.png?X-Amz-Algorithm=AWS4-HMAC-SHA256&X-Amz-Content-Sha256=UNSIGNED-PAYLOAD&X-Amz-Credential=ASIAZI2LB466UWH6YDSB%2F20260324%2Fus-west-2%2Fs3%2Faws4_request&X-Amz-Date=20260324T145512Z&X-Amz-Expires=3600&X-Amz-Security-Token=IQoJb3JpZ2luX2VjEM%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FwEaCXVzLXdlc3QtMiJHMEUCIQCqxXdtVJkhEky1MOiYhVvfbwZNK7n4I0vgzCHBTVVMSQIgVoy5kaXu9KqdjCltLXS6LdrIbbtd7W5kjDp5vYuxeqMqiAQImP%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2F%2FARAAGgw2Mzc0MjMxODM4MDUiDFzcqYrCnNGcA7Yy9CrcA5g3RogEhPEsIQ5K4fpeR%2F50uXOu%2BMq1Y0p%2BN%2FVjbAAkvHUEaYQjwUzrJ01tmYNM2J6ogigjcED%2FjAiitlk65X%2BHJ1jKJe5LOapMYglAXShwhEuT3zarahg9np854ISfzr7RJNTx%2B7FDQiVwviCTEIPS1R21kux0T1aH%2BklzjV2ZFYH04Xvxeq%2Bs%2BijVtz5Et%2FjQvE3b8qWHz0joWmXNV%2FjPB2GqoNqahjCvzXk42KA6jXQxSb%2FF9Qdki%2F1PA6jhv4%2BtLnw56Rt7nAr0K5xe7RvB6IbebPy2dwRiXBkCYWr3TipGzcl3fKiNK0WhqTDrkhHY0LY1IaSYeYrcL1%2BMr%2FBPFdnh3V8UXH3rxN5uyoEz5A%2Bj04j%2BxLu%2BE07XeGOZGNcHvibFHT2VrEOJj%2BbbwGY6Cbi%2B4IhWKNhYxg2OnqOYDqxPTNLf0z%2BuhRoQQCWebTH%2FBpaoSP%2BAhPBZRYv3qeGiuhge45w6wCTJ4kUEdt%2BAyi3DTe10gyiQ%2F5vQ4z5avpcXoX9Vb%2Bsf4m%2F2SBghmduixvILqZMvYYqwtv8WLBkWk6yyU1Zt%2BT47OorBerdEQly47wUx7dwywAeJ3jtYu4M23Wf1XZs0fMQX%2BxY%2Bcg%2BBkFiPbzukFW2uECiIMJ7Ais4GOqUBacEjj8GpbD83pteKKVeMC8xgE0gMcMoSiw00InE1zIb%2Bp2AtzV5Y5CY2ASf5gMUNFSbWWO1Rvo6TDNvd86qaNCPYKdJvolf7IAQvTWGkdHpFdMOqVCnYWLudv3grGoIv%2BE00qP5Sa9Oyrk%2FXhY7fEuVqigALxDTuOFWFkM2tjr2jfCpe03MXA1lCXIKFISKezRn%2BRaxSjaZg9wsi21mM%2BHaLYaBj&X-Amz-Signature=9158848296c5cb7fcc51da9e32186b0c264584da969c2381598708bb5ff3dfdb&X-Amz-SignedHeaders=host&x-amz-checksum-mode=ENABLED&x-id=GetObject",
      "caption": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "✅ 2. Confirmation Dialogs"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Problem: Actions occurred immediately without warnings."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Solution:"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "We introduced confirmation modals that included:"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Clear warning messages about consequences",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Optional checkboxes for sensitive deletions",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Clear button options: “Cancel” (non-destructive), “Confirm Delete” (destructive)",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "✅ 3. Visual Differentiation"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Problem: Destructive buttons visually blended with other controls."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Solution:"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Used high-contrast red color with text + icon (e.g., 🗑️ DELETE)",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Avoided placing destructive actions next to primary buttons",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Styled destructive actions as secondary, except within confirmation dialogs",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "✅ 4. Accessibility Compliance"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Problem: Buttons failed to meet basic WCAG standards."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Solution:"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "We updated destructive buttons to meet:"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Target size of at least 24×24px (WCAG 2.5.8)",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Contrast ratio ≥ 4.5:1 between text and background (WCAG 1.4.3)",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Focus visibility (WCAG 2.4.7) with clear outlines and spacing",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "We also tested with assistive technologies to ensure compatibility."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "Results"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "92% reduction in support tickets related to accidental deletion.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Improved task completion rates in usability tests.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Positive qualitative feedback from users: “I feel much safer using this now.”",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Design system updated with clear patterns for destructive actions, adopted across multiple teams.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": ""
    },
    {
      "type": "h3",
      "text": "Key Takeaways"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Destructive buttons must be designed with caution: clear labels, confirmation dialogs, and accessible styles are non-negotiable.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Accessibility is not a layer on top—it’s part of the design from the beginning.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    },
    {
      "type": "li",
      "text": "Small improvements (like button spacing and contrast) significantly impact user trust and safety.",
      "listType": "bullet"
    }
  ]
}